padding:64px 28px 0; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; border:3px solid #e8112d; background:#1a0306; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b, 0 0 28px rgba(232,17,45,0.55); padding:14px 22px; margin-bottom:46px;\">\n        <span style=\"width:0;height:0;border-left:13px solid #ff1f3d;border-top:8px solid transparent;border-bottom:8px solid transparent;\"><\u002Fspan>\n        <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#ff1f3d; letter-spacing:2px;\">SEASON SIMULATION<\u002Fspan>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <h1 style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:clamp(40px,8vw,92px); line-height:1.08; margin:0; letter-spacing:1px; text-shadow:5px 5px 0 #7a0a18, 9px 9px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.6);\">\n        <span style=\"color:#f4f0e6;\">MATTER<\u002Fspan><br>\n        <span style=\"color:#ff1f3d;\">OF<\u002Fspan><br>\n        <span style=\"color:#f4f0e6;\">PRINCIPLE<\u002Fspan>\n      <\u002Fh1>\n\n      <div style=\"position:relative; height:200px; margin:34px auto 18px; max-width:620px;\">\n        <div style=\"position:absolute; left:50%; bottom:34px; transform:translateX(-50%); width:560px; height:14px; background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,#3a3a44 0 22px, transparent 22px 44px); opacity:.5;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n        <img src=\"ae01d7f8-90f8-4931-a094-721c891c5ef2\" alt=\"red race car\" style=\"position:absolute; left:50%; bottom:30px; width:360px; transform:translateX(-50%); animation:mop-drive 3.6s ease-in-out infinite; filter:drop-shadow(0 14px 14px rgba(232,17,45,0.35));\">\n        <img src=\"6d7606da-0875-4b1d-b4e3-66d3a2328be4\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute; right:6%; top:6px; width:54px; animation:mop-spin 7s linear infinite;\">\n        <img src=\"6d7606da-0875-4b1d-b4e3-66d3a2328be4\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute; left:7%; top:34px; width:36px; animation:mop-spin 9s linear infinite reverse;\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <p style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:21px; color:#ffb300; letter-spacing:2px; margin:26px 0 30px; text-shadow:3px 3px 0 #6b4a00;\">YOUR TEAM IS IN CRISIS.<\u002Fp>\n\n      <p style=\"max-width:620px; margin:0 auto 40px; font-size:20px; line-height:1.85; color:#c9c4ba; font-weight:500;\">\n        Rararacing is about to go bankrupt. Nobody wants to sail the sinking ship. Your friend from its executives board is begging for a favor — take over team principal's role and lead the boat out of the storm.\n      <\u002Fp>\n\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:18px; justify-content:center; align-items:stretch;\">\n        <a href=\"#play\" style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; text-decoration:none; background:#e8112d; border:3px solid #ff5066; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b, 0 6px 0 #7a0a18, 0 6px 24px rgba(232,17,45,0.5); padding:20px 34px;\">\n          <span style=\"width:0;height:0;border-left:15px solid #fff;border-top:9px solid transparent;border-bottom:9px solid transparent;\"><\u002Fspan>\n          <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#fff; letter-spacing:1px;\">START SEASON<\u002Fspan>\n        <\u002Fa>\n        <a href=\"#play\" style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; text-decoration:none; background:#0e1420; border:3px solid #2a3b55; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b; padding:20px 30px;\">\n          <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#cdd6e6; letter-spacing:1px;\">HOW TO PLAY<\u002Fspan>\n        <\u002Fa>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <p style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:15px; color:#4a4a55; letter-spacing:2px; margin-top:52px;\">SEASON 01 · RARARACING MOTORSPORTS<\u002Fp>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ THE GARAGE ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"Garage\" style=\"position:relative; padding:74px 0 80px; background:\n      linear-gradient(180deg,#08080b 0%, #0c0d12 100%);\n      border-top:3px solid #16171e;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width:1080px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 28px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:18px; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:14px;\">\n        <img src=\"254f8f2e-3d2f-4234-b47a-241cac90ad84\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:42px; animation:mop-spin 4s linear infinite;\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:clamp(22px,3.4vw,34px); color:#29b6d8; letter-spacing:1px; margin:0; text-shadow:3px 3px 0 #0b4150;\">THE GARAGE<\u002Fh2>\n        <img src=\"254f8f2e-3d2f-4234-b47a-241cac90ad84\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:42px; animation:mop-spin 4s linear infinite reverse;\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <p style=\"text-align:center; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 50px; font-size:19px; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4ba; font-weight:500;\">Three liveries warming up in the pit lane. Burn the budget into car development and watch your machine claw its way up the grid.<\u002Fp>\n\n      <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr)); gap:26px;\">\n\n        <div style=\"background:#120406; border:3px solid #e8112d; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b, 0 0 26px rgba(232,17,45,0.3); padding:30px 24px 26px; text-align:center;\">\n          <div style=\"height:120px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;\"><img src=\"ae01d7f8-90f8-4931-a094-721c891c5ef2\" alt=\"red car\" style=\"width:230px; animation:mop-bob 3s ease-in-out infinite;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:15px; color:#ff1f3d; margin-top:16px; letter-spacing:1px;\">SCARLET<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-size:16px; color:#8f8a80; margin-top:10px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:1px;\">FLAGSHIP CHASSIS<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <div style=\"background:#120d02; border:3px solid #ffb300; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b, 0 0 26px rgba(255,179,0,0.28); padding:30px 24px 26px; text-align:center;\">\n          <div style=\"height:120px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;\"><img src=\"742657c6-3ea2-4649-80fa-e8986020fabb\" alt=\"gold car\" style=\"width:230px; animation:mop-bob 3s ease-in-out infinite .4s;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:15px; color:#ffc61a; margin-top:16px; letter-spacing:1px;\">BULLION<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-size:16px; color:#8f8a80; margin-top:10px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:1px;\">SPONSOR MAGNET<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <div style=\"background:#02100f; border:3px solid #29b6d8; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b, 0 0 26px rgba(41,182,216,0.28); padding:30px 24px 26px; text-align:center;\">\n          <div style=\"height:120px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;\"><img src=\"2f029722-b71a-49b8-a92c-e1dfa87b3e3a\" alt=\"teal car\" style=\"width:230px; animation:mop-bob 3s ease-in-out infinite .8s;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:15px; color:#37cdec; margin-top:16px; letter-spacing:1px;\">AZURE<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-size:16px; color:#8f8a80; margin-top:10px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:1px;\">HIGH-RISK RUNNER<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ HOW TO PLAY ============ -->\n  <section id=\"play\" data-screen-label=\"How to Play\" style=\"position:relative; padding:78px 0 84px; background:\n      radial-gradient(120% 70% at 50% 0%, #14100a 0%, #08080b 60%); border-top:3px solid #16171e;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width:980px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 28px;\">\n\n      <div style=\"text-align:center; margin-bottom:18px;\">\n        <div style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; border:3px solid #ffb300; background:#0f0a02; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b, 0 0 28px rgba(255,179,0,0.4); padding:16px 26px;\">\n          <span style=\"width:18px; height:18px; background:#ffb300; display:inline-block;\"><\u002Fspan>\n          <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:22px; color:#ffc61a; letter-spacing:2px;\">HOW TO PLAY<\u002Fspan>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <p style=\"text-align:center; font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:14px; color:#f4f0e6; letter-spacing:3px; margin:0 0 50px;\">GAME LOOP<\u002Fp>\n\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:20px;\">\n\n        <!-- 01 -->\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0; border:3px solid #2a3b55; background:#0b0c11; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:none; width:108px; background:#120406; border-right:3px solid #e8112d; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px; padding:14px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:22px; color:#ff1f3d;\">01<\u002Fspan>\n            <img src=\"30ae02f7-7c0e-476c-8335-07b6f10ef024\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:50px;\">\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:22px 26px;\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#ffc61a; letter-spacing:1px; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.4;\">NAME YOUR TEAM &amp; PICK A DRIVER<\u002Fh3>\n            <p style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4ba; font-weight:500; margin:0;\">You start with 100M G (Geld). First, name your team. Then choose one of three drivers — each has a skill index (0–10) and a cost deducted immediately from your budget.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <!-- 02 -->\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0; border:3px solid #2a3b55; background:#0b0c11; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:none; width:108px; background:#0f0a02; border-right:3px solid #ffb300; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px; padding:14px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:22px; color:#ff1f3d;\">02<\u002Fspan>\n            <img src=\"e58ab7b8-8fb3-4ea4-8d2d-7467ca6e358b\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:46px;\">\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:22px 26px;\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#ffc61a; letter-spacing:1px; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.4;\">INVEST BEFORE EACH RACE<\u002Fh3>\n            <p style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4ba; font-weight:500; margin:0;\">Allocate Geld into car development, staff quality, and public image. The impact of each category is displayed in the key formulas section.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <!-- 03 -->\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0; border:3px solid #2a3b55; background:#0b0c11; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:none; width:108px; background:#02100f; border-right:3px solid #29b6d8; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px; padding:14px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:22px; color:#ff1f3d;\">03<\u002Fspan>\n            <img src=\"5fdf0ace-6afa-4051-a9c2-8bcbac031344\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:46px;\">\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:22px 26px;\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#ffc61a; letter-spacing:1px; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.4;\">SET YOUR RISK WILLINGNESS<\u002Fh3>\n            <p style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4ba; font-weight:500; margin:0;\">High risk high reward is our slogan. Risk is an integral part of racing, you have to decide weather you wanna go all in.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <!-- 04 -->\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0; border:3px solid #2a3b55; background:#0b0c11; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:none; width:108px; background:#0a0f14; border-right:3px solid #f4f0e6; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px; padding:14px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:22px; color:#ff1f3d;\">04<\u002Fspan>\n            <img src=\"22a315c7-d893-4f15-a634-32c0216af4bb\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:50px;\">\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:22px 26px;\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#ffc61a; letter-spacing:1px; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.4;\">RACE THE CALENDAR<\u002Fh3>\n            <p style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4ba; font-weight:500; margin:0;\">8 races across Paris, Strassburg, Stuttgart, Vienna, Budapest, Bucharest, Sinaia, and Istanbul. Your race score is calculated from car performance, driver skill, and strategy and determines your place.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <!-- 05 -->\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0; border:3px solid #2a3b55; background:#0b0c11; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:none; width:108px; background:#0f0a02; border-right:3px solid #ffb300; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px; padding:14px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:22px; color:#ff1f3d;\">05<\u002Fspan>\n            <img src=\"5d58b7d8-b4bc-4365-9bcd-ae1b0b45dd28\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:42px;\">\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:22px 26px;\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#ffc61a; letter-spacing:1px; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.4;\">COMPETE &amp; COLLECT PRIZE MONEY<\u002Fh3>\n            <p style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4ba; font-weight:500; margin:0;\">You race against 9 rival teams. Finishing position determines your prize money — 1st place pays 50M G, 10th pays 1M G. Rivals develop their cars between races, so staying ahead gets harder.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <!-- 06 -->\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0; border:3px solid #2a3b55; background:#0b0c11; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:none; width:108px; background:#120406; border-right:3px solid #e8112d; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px; padding:14px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:22px; color:#ff1f3d;\">06<\u002Fspan>\n            <img src=\"6d7606da-0875-4b1d-b4e3-66d3a2328be4\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:48px; animation:mop-spin 6s linear infinite;\">\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:22px 26px;\">\n            <h3 style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:18px; color:#ffc61a; letter-spacing:1px; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.4;\">MANAGE CRASHES &amp; SPONSORS<\u002Fh3>\n            <p style=\"font-size:18px; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4ba; font-weight:500; margin:0;\">High risk means crash losses subtracted from your budget after each race. Obviously, public image explicitly affects sponsorships — the higher it is, the more likely you are to land a contract that race.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <!-- 07 -->\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0; border:3px solid #2a3b55; background:#0b0c11; box-shadow:0 0 0 4px #08080b;\">\n          <div style=\"flex:none; width:108px; background:#02100f; border-right:3px solid #29b6d8; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px; padding:14px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace; font-size:22px; color:#ff1f3d;\">07<\u002Fspan>\n            <img src=\"2291f0e7-5b05-41a0-82f4-52dbbafac05a\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:48px;\">\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:2